Who here does not have<br>the time to get to know Julie?
<SYNC Start=1022419><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1022688><P Class=ENCC>
I got the time to get to know Julie.
<SYNC Start=1025020><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1027292><P Class=ENCC>
