My brother's straight, so....
<SYNC Start=1053048><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1054620><P Class=ENCC>
Here you go.
<SYNC Start=1055985><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1056221><P Class=ENCC>
You know what?<br>I just have one more question.
<SYNC Start=1058781><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1059191><P Class=ENCC>
If you had figured this out sooner,<br>and I had been around...
