<SYNC Start=1068967><P Class=ENCC>
No. Don't tell me.
<SYNC Start=1070161><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1070402><P Class=ENCC>
I don't think either answer<br>would make me feel better. Here.
<SYNC Start=1074361><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1076375><P Class=ENCC>
I love you, Phoebe.
<SYNC Start=1077535><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1092858><P Class=ENCC>
