<SYNC Start=1096829><P Class=ENCC>
Seriously.
<SYNC Start=1097921><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1101433><P Class=ENCC>
and my second-grade teacher<br>was Miss Thomas...
<SYNC Start=1104834><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1105037><P Class=ENCC>
